=head1 DESCRIPTION

Creates settings for the require check in feature that are applied to a
room profile. Require check in allows a meeting roomE<rsquo>s Alexa or
AVS device to prompt the user to check in; otherwise, the room will be
released.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Enabled => Bool

Whether require check in is enabled or not.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ReleaseAfterMinutes => Int

Duration between 5 and 20 minutes to determine when to release the room
if it's not checked into.



